observations.recommendation:
We recommended that management:
1. Together with the Local School Board, to give priority to programs, activities and projects enumerated in Section 272 of RA 7160 in the budget preparation of the SEF budget;

2. Require the requesting agencies for supplies and other goods to submit their Project Procurement Management Plans (PPMP) to the BAC Secretariat for the inclusion of the PPMP in the Annual Procurement Plan/Supplemental Procurement Plan;

3. Strictly adhere to the provision in Section 305(a) of RA 7160.

